Would consider trades. 

Size 9.5 great condition for such a sought after, rare dunk. Not willing to do half off for this shoe. 

Hit me up on Tradeblock if you want to trade. (chillwill) Not in a rush to get rid of these.

Selling 90% of my collection. Plenty of deals. If you bundle 2 or more items I give 50% off. Steals!!

Trying to list a new pair EVERY DAY. Bundle for incredible prices. If you want all my shoes (~90 pairs: dunks, SBs, jordans, vintage skate shoes, AF1, and more), let me know and I can make you a price for all.

I will be trying to list a new pair of shoes every other day. Be sure to follow my page for the best chance at some RARE shoes and great deals. Throw an offer or bundle for discount.

Also selling Etnies, Emerica, Lakai, Jordans, AJF, Jordan Fusion, Timberlands, Nike SB, Nike FC, Nike 6.0, Prod, Air Force Ones, Supreme, Kobes, Adidas, Nike Dunks, Forum, Janoski, Doernbecher, Jordan Spizike [SOLD], Adidas Forum, Adio, AF1 Air Force One, Nike SB, Kobe, Air Max, Nike rare Dunks, Nike KD Durant BHM Black History Month Betta, vintage skate shoes, and more. Have many shoes for sale, adding more daily. These range from Air Force Ones, Jordans, Kobes, Adidas, Dunks, SBs, Janoski, and vintage skate shoes. Only thing I don't have is Yeezy.

Buy one pair at full price and second pair is half off.
